{"tid":1480183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［強國崛起］4間中國大學2019排行世界TOP100，港大中大排100以外","createTime":"2019-08-17T07:49:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T08:12:41.000Z","uid":152084,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"7b70e9660258beb799ea79815714dca87bdcb67c","tid":1480183,"uid":152084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:49:32.000Z","msg":"微博熱搜第一位：中國四間大學進入全球前100名。<br />\n<br />\n一開始睇到個排名都覺得算合理，睇睇係發現港大中大排100以外，仲要比浙江大學落後。好啦，咁就睇下呢個排名係咩機構，個排名榜就咁叫&lsquo;世界大學學術排名&rsquo;，英文簡稱ARWU，哇好似好權威。跟著上網查一查呢個機構，<span style=\"color: red;\">原來個排行榜係由一間上海教育公司負責，簡稱上海排名</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BMPVCLu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBMPVCLu.png&h=77bee060&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y6JrKqv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY6JrKqv.png&h=9145bd9c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ixaUTiR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FixaUTiR.png&h=077dd731&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.sina.cn/2019-08-17/detail-ihytcern1444518.d.html?from=wap&amp;wm=3049_0015&amp;hd=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sina.cn%2F2019-08-17%2Fdetail-ihytcern1444518.d.html%3Ffrom%3Dwap%26wm%3D3049_0015%26hd%3D1&d=9fV5YN%2BdLeg0vJDpI0pnms%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=0edf181c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.sina.cn/2019-08-17/detail-ihytcern1444518.d.html?from=wap&amp;wm=3049_0015&amp;hd=1</a><br />\n<br />\n中國人活係自己世界裡面，你们中国人开心就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bdf8e302c310b64213ea5dd6e69fb957dd26bb5","tid":1480183,"uid":79046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:50:34.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，借一借位<img src=\"/assets/fa